title: Charming Marina 1BR – Just Two Blocks to Chestnut Street!
posting_body: ['Charming Marina 1BR – Just Two Blocks to Chestnut Street!', 'Property Address', '40 Capra Way | 01 | San Francisco, CA 94123', 'Available: Now', 'Offered By', 'Gaetani Real Estate', 'Description', '$3,195 | 40', 'Capra #1, San Francisco, CA 94123', 'This spacious one-bedroom Edwardian style apartment is ideally located steps from Chestnut Street, Marina Green & The Palace of Fine Arts.', 'This residence is on the quiet rear side of the building and boasts a large eat-in-kitchen, two walk-in closets and hardwood floors throughout the living room & bedroom.', 'This must-see apartment exudes San Francisco charm!', 'Walk Score: 92 (Walkers Paradise)', 'KEY FEATURES:', '- Eat-in-kitchen', '- Hardwood floors throughout the living room & bedroom', '- Two large walk-in closets', '- Large scale bedroom & living space', '- Period details and tons of San Francisco charm!', 'TERMS:', '1 year lease', 'Water & garbage included, tenant pays PG&E', 'Contact Brett for more information or to schedule a tour!', 'Brett van den Eikhof', 'DRE #01910306', 'brett@gaetanirealestate <URL>)', 'This unit is a rental unit subject to the San Francisco Rent Ordinance, which limits evictions without just cause, and which states that any waiver by tenant of their rights under the rent ordinance is void as contrary to public policy.', 'Amenities', 'Coin-op laundry', 'Details', 'Beds/Baths: 1BD/1.0BA', 'Rental Terms', 'Rent: $3,195.00', 'Available: Now', 'Application Fee: $40.00', 'Security Deposit: $3,695.00', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats not allowed', 'Dogs not allowed']
